name: Aircraft Pack: B717, MD87 & MD90
description:
Brings MD87/MD90/B717 to ACEO. Not functional without ACEOTweaks-Core and ACEOTweaks-Aircraft. This aircrafts will only spawn from airline mods which include them. 
 
 Known Issue: Cleaning Truck on MD87 and B717 will still spawn at the back on non existing door and do not have enough space between wingn and engine to attach
author: dawed
